snippet.title: Squid Game: Unleashed | Official Soundtrack | Netflix Games
snippet.description:
Composer Stephen Rippy explains how he brought the original music to life for Squid Game: Unleashed. From live instruments to a female choir, the eclectic soundtrack was recorded at Synchron Stage in Vienna and mixed at Skywalker Sound in Nicasio, CA.

The soundtrack is now available to stream and download wherever you get your music!

Pre-register for Squid Game: Unleashed on the App Store and Google Play, and unlock an exclusive skin during global launch. Show off your style as you face off against players across the world in a battle for glory. Squid Game: Unleashed will be available exclusively in the Netflix App. Pre-register now at squidgameunleashed.com

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 283 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Squid Game: Unleashed | Official Soundtrack | Netflix Games
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

You win some, you die some. Use skill and killer instinct to survive twisted competitions in this multiplayer action game inspired by the hit series.
